data.description: Nestled in the heart of a mature neighborhood, 8111 Mescal Trail in San Antonio, TX 78244 stands as a beacon of modernity and comfort. This expansive 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom abode spans 2521 square feet of meticulously designed living space, boasting both elegance and functionality.    Approaching the residence, you're greeted by the shade of majestic mature trees, lending a sense of tranquility and privacy. The exterior, adorned with timeless 4-sided brick, exudes a classic charm that seamlessly integrates with the surrounding landscape.    Step inside to discover a sanctuary of luxury and convenience. The absence of carpet and the presence of gleaming hardwood floors downstairs and resilient vinyl flooring upstairs offer both durability and aesthetic appeal, promising easy maintenance and a touch of sophistication.    Entertainment and relaxation intertwine effortlessly in the backyard oasis, featuring a charming gazebo-a perfect spot for alfresco dining or serene lounging. With solar panels adorning the roof, this home is not only environmentally conscious but also economically savvy, reducing energy costs and carbon footprint.    Safety and peace of mind are paramount, thanks to the state-of-the-art security system equipped with a thermostat, motion sensors, and cameras-all seamlessly controllable via a user-friendly app. Whether you're at home or away, rest assured knowing that your sanctuary is safeguarded with cutting-edge technology.    Conveniently situated near FM 78 on a burgeoning side of town, this residence offers proximity to a host of amenities, from shopping and dining to recreational opportunities. Plus, with a 1-year-old HVAC system and water heater boasting a 5-year warranty, as well as a water softener and a 10-year warranty on the roof, this home ensures not only comfort but also long-term peace of mind.    In essence, 8111 Mescal Trail embodies the perfect fusion of modern luxury, timeless charm, and practicality-a haven where every detail is meticulously crafted to elevate your lifestyle and fulfill your dreams of home.
